# SHELDON Executive Intelligence System - Webhook Documentation

## Overview
This document contains all webhook endpoints configured for the SHELDON Executive Intelligence Dashboard used by AmeriQual Foods. Webhooks are HTTP endpoints that enable communication between the dashboard and backend services.

---

## WEBHOOK INVENTORY

### 1. CORE COMMUNICATION WEBHOOKS

#### Chat Webhook
- **URL:** https://hook.us2.make.com/3eftqahiejqpw3yr2va4993aqkdoipgs
- **Status:** ACTIVE
- **Purpose:** Handles all conversational AI interactions with the SHELDON system
- **Functionality:** Processes user queries, commands, and requests. Returns AI-generated responses based on the user's input, current KPIs, and recent alerts.
- **Data Sent:** User command, chat mode, user name, timestamp, current KPIs, recent alerts

#### Text-to-Speech (TTS) Webhook
- **URL:** https://hook.us2.make.com/lypllp614zvrjplgpm16lhzbk7heykgm
- **Status:** ACTIVE
- **Purpose:** Converts text responses to audio for voice playback
- **Functionality:** Takes text input and returns an audio blob that can be played through the browser
- **Data Sent:** Text content to be converted to speech

