## TECHNICAL NOTES

### Webhook Platform
All webhooks are hosted on Make.com (formerly Integromat) using the hook.us2.make.com domain.

### Authentication
Webhook endpoints should be secured with appropriate authentication tokens (not shown in configuration).

### Data Format
All webhooks use JSON format for request/response data with Content-Type: application/json headers.

### Error Handling
The dashboard includes fallback behavior when webhooks are not configured or unavailable, using simulated data for demonstration purposes.

---

## SUMMARY

- **Total Webhooks Defined:** 35
- **Currently Active:** 2 (Chat and TTS)
- **Pending Configuration:** 33

The two active webhooks handle the core conversational AI functionality, while the remaining webhooks are placeholders for expanded functionality as the system is developed.
